{"type": "article", "id": 19872, "title": "法式扑克牌", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-29T07:40:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 103, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071149495oLmYZaeHWhEqUig.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这幅扑克牌来自匈牙利的设计师 Krisztina Berta，他想挑战传统扑克牌呆板的造型。他将四种花色都做出了带有几何感的图案，原本黑桃、红桃、梅花上的圆润感都被切尖了。而 J、Q、K 和大小王上的人像都用流动的线条勾勒出来，非常艺术。此外，扑克牌整体用了浅黄和深蓝两种颜色来代替红和黑，图像中也没有其他的颜色，简洁而优雅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150228vBRVy1che9tnXSfk.gif\" width=\"600\" height=\"360\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150230scywv49tGMHf8LAp.gif\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150231KRcN0mBpDOT5wrnI.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"764\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150232M6Ap58G4e1Yq2JOr.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"764\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261502332TLqaFCVWQiGk5Bd.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"648\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}